window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Xaros broke against Earth's defenses, but the war may be lost. </p> <p>The alien ships of former allies rule Earth's skies, threatening to obliterate cities and turn the planet into a barren wasteland if humanity refuses their demands. </p> <p>With their backs to the wall, the scattered crew of the Breitenfeld must work together to foil the enemy's plan before time runs out. </p> <p>The path to freedom leads through <i>The Crucible</i>. </p>"; 
